          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Wealth and Investment Planning\nOverview\nDirect Investing\nGuided Portfolios\nWealth and Investment Planning\neTerm Deposits\nRegistered Plans\nAt Alterna, we want to help you build a unique and professionally managed financial solution that creates and preserves wealth for you and your family for years to come. Backed by a team of investment industry experts, our Wealth Advisors will work with you to develop your investment strategy, retirement plan, education savings and more to make sure you have the tools and knowledge you need to reach your financial goals.",
